o. Miraflores Temas: todos excepto contexto y cultura y situaci\u00f3n actual y su contexto 07/07/15 Miraflores 8 Meyer Flores Nolazco. Miraflores Temas: todos los 11 temas 07/07/15 Miraflores 9 An\u00edbal Santiago Chihu\u00e1n. Miraflores Temas: todos excepto situaci\u00f3n actual y su contexto 07/07/15 Miraflores 10 Jacinto Jim\u00e9nez \u00c1lvaro. RPNYC Temas: todos 08/07/15 Miraflores 11 Priscilo Ruiz Abarca. Miraflores Temas: todos 08/07/15 Miraflores 12 Jos\u00e9 Ruiz Palomares. RPNYC Temas: Todos los 11 temas 10/07/15 Canchayllo 13 N\u00e9rida Bera\u00fan Huam\u00e1n.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "81d5335c-a9a8-4d02-b245-41934ae7fe12": {"__data__": {"id_": "81d5335c-a9a8-4d02-b245-41934ae7fe12", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/informe-de-sistematizacion-de-la-experiencia", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Informe de sistematizaci\u00f3n de la experiencia", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/informe-de-sistematizacion-de-la-experiencia", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "565d887be17aabdff4dd0a4ec37cbb8baa5121ba3ccb67aea14138594295fe1f"}, "2": {"node_id": "a46cc98d-c602-4c50-ba5f-b07e06e46f07", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/informe-de-sistematizacion-de-la-experiencia", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type